reviewText: I really like the movie because it was uplifting and moving. A positive movie
Great movie for the family. Funny and entertaining movie, great for all ages. The little girl (Abbey) is an amazing actress!
This is a heart warming film about how love can change, and save, a life. If you have a soul, you'll enjoy it!
This is a heartwarming and inspirational Movie for the whole family. It's a must see!!
